msgid "Data complying with the specifications listed in table 16."
msgstr ""

#: ../../SO2.md:142
msgid "A pool of national experts officially nominated by the national authorities to verify the suitability and consistency of the default data against the situation in their country, or to identify and compile data using national sources for the indicator. Key institutions might include a country’s national statistical office, ministry of health and ministry of water resources, as well as universities and research centres."
